{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTML5 跨瀏覽器兼容程式碼","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/orphaned/HTML5_Cross_Browser_Polyfills","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>這是個蒐集中文世界開發（但不一定原創）的跨瀏覽器兼容代碼、連結的地方，作為 Paul Irish<a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://github.com/Modernizr/Modernizr/wiki/HTML5-Cross-browser-Polyfills\" title=\"https://github.com/Modernizr/Modernizr/wiki/HTML5-Cross-browser-Polyfills\" rel=\" noopener\">《HTML5 Cross Browser Polyfills》</a>的仿效文件。蒐集不會完全，因此也強烈建議繼續追蹤上述文件的進展，或是使用搜尋引擎。</p>\n<p>歡迎貢獻新的代碼、連結，不過請注意放在這個地方的代碼皆屬於<a class=\"external\" href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%89%E9%A0%98%E5%9F%9F\" title=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/公有領域\" rel=\" noopener\">公有領域</a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"全頻（fullscreen）api","title":"全頻（fullscreen）API","isH3":false,"content":"<p>支援&nbsp; Gecko:FullScreenAPI 草案的 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/fullScreen\"><code>window.fullScreen</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 與 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/fullscreenchange_event\"><code>fullscreenchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 事件 ，由<a class=\"external\" href=\"http://hax.iteye.com/\" title=\"http://hax.iteye.com/\" rel=\" noopener\">贺师俊</a>（hax）所<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/public-html-ig-zh/2011Aug/0005\" title=\"http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/public-html-ig-zh/2011Aug/0005\" rel=\" noopener\">提供</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'fullScreen'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">defineProperty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'fullScreen'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">get</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>screen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>width <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>outerWidth <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> screen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>height <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>outerHeight<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> _fullScreen <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fullScreen\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'onfullscreenchange'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'resize'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> f <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fullScreen\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>f <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> _fullScreen<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    _fullScreen <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> f\n    <span class=\"token function\">fireSimpleEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'fullscreenchange'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token literal-property property\">bubbles</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">fireSimpleEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">type<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> target<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> option</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> target <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>option<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> option <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> evt <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Event'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  evt<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">initEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>type<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>option<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bubbles<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>option<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cancelable<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">dispatchEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>evt<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"中文排版","title":"中文排版","isH3":false,"content":"<ul> <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://ethantw.net/projects/han/\" title=\"http://ethantw.net/projects/han/\" rel=\" noopener\">漢字標準格式・CSS Reset</a>（Ethan） <ul> <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ruby\"><code>&lt;ruby&gt;</code></a>（上測、右側）、用 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/em\"><code>&lt;em&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 達到著重號的效果（CSS 屬性 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/text-emphasis\"><code>text-emphasis</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>），非 CSS 模擬。</li> </ul> </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"全頻（fullscreen）API","id":"全頻（fullscreen）api"},{"text":"中文排版","id":"中文排版"}],"summary":"這是個蒐集中文世界開發（但不一定原創）的跨瀏覽器兼容代碼、連結的地方，作為 Paul Irish《HTML5 Cross Browser Polyfills》的仿效文件。蒐集不會完全，因此也強烈建議繼續追蹤上述文件的進展，或是使用搜尋引擎。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","source":{"folder":"zh-tw/orphaned/html5_cross_browser_polyfills","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/orphaned/html5_cross_browser_polyfills/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"HTML5 跨瀏覽器兼容程式碼 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}